examples.en: Sounds like a jolly good idea to me.
examples.ru: Как по мне, это очень хорошая мысль.

examples.en: It was all jolly good fun.
Come and have a "jolly" with us.

examples.en: She had a jolly time at the party.

examples.en: They eat and drink, and live jolly in the open air.

examples.en: Right, I'm going to clear up, and you can jolly well help me.
